ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Foreign Affairs of BOB PLAMONDON of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective May 14, 2014, in the place of Robert Tennant.
